Analysis of ODU Fee
Structure
Group Members: Mounika Kompalli
Sindhuja Gadde
Sruta Keerti Kasula
Brief reminder of our project topic:
Our project idea is taken from Mace & Crown to help them analyze ODU fee structure.
This project implements the following tasks:
1) Where is ODU standing among all other universities in Virginia with respect to fees?
2) Breakdown of student fees that each student pays every semester.
3) Fee trend in last 10 years.
